1. *Baru* sam se oženio prošlog meseca. (I just got married last month.)
2. Išli smo u kafanu *baru* večeras. (We went to the bar tonight.)
3. Imao sam *baru* problema sa računarom. (I had some computer problems.)
4. *Baru* ću odlučiti da li da ostavim posao. (I will soon decide whether to leave the job.)
5. Ona *baru* pokuša da dobije posao. (She recently tried to get a job.)